description:
If you are a big nerd like me who loves not only The Great British Bake Off and Jameela Jamil, please enjoy this absolute joy I found while poking about youtube.

Highlights include: Jameela having no idea what she’s doing but doing better than she thought, Michael Sheen and his adventures in shortbread (and his adorable WALES 4 EVER poster) and David Mitchell’s massive meringue (this is not a euphemism)..

caption:
GOOD OMENS: Neil Gaiman’s Post-Production Update Ahead Of 2019 Launch

Good Omens co-author and showrunner Neil Gaiman has provided an update on the status of the six-episode adaptation of the much-loved novel. Neil has been working on the series since late 2017 and tells in his new blog post That Was The 2018 That Was how Good Omens dominated his life throughout the year and will continue to do so into 2019.

Create Artwork For Amazon Prime's Good Omens  

Amazon Prime have sent out a request to all the artists out there - they are...
caption:
Create Artwork For Amazon Prime’s Good Omens 

Amazon Prime have sent out a request to all the artists out there - they are looking for fan-created images to promote the much anticipated series Good Omens across their social media next year.

Amazon have teamed up with US based art networking site Talenthouse to launch a search for original poster artwork to celebrate the release of the six-part comedy Good Omens on Amazon Prime early next year. Illustrators, designers and graphic artists worldwide are encouraged to find inspiration in the unlikely pairing of angel and devil duo Aziraphale and Crowley and create art that can be used across Good Omens’ key social channels and displayed at events.

Continue reading
